author: admin
title: Teradata Announces 2015 Third Quarter Earnings Release Date
text:
Submitted by admin on 9/24/2015 @ 2:30 PM   Teradata Corp. 
ATLANTA, Sept. 24, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- Teradata Corp. (NYSE: TDC ) today announced that it will release its 2015 third quarter financial results before the market opens on November 5, 2015. Teradata will host a conference call and live web broadcast at 8:30 a.m. ET the same day to discuss the results. 
The live web broadcast and replay will be available on the Teradata website at investor.teradata.com http://www.teradata.com/investor . 
About Teradata Teradata's leading portfolio of big data analytic solutions, integrated marketing applications, and services can help organizations gain a sustainable competitive advantage with data. Visit teradata.com .
